<NomaiObject>
	<TextBlock>
		<ID>1</ID>
		<Text>YARROW: Some time has passed since I checked in with you, Pye. How are you and Idaea progressing with the <![CDATA[<color=orange>Sun Station</color>]]> plans?</Text>
	</TextBlock>
	<TextBlock>
		<ID>2</ID>
		<ParentID>1</ParentID>
		<Text>PYE: Presently, my assessment is that our plan will either fail explosively or succeed explosively.</Text>
