	</TextBlock>
	<TextBlock>
		<ID>5</ID>
		<ParentID>4</ParentID>
		<Text>IDAEA: I don’t see what state of matter you are has to do with this. And I don’t recall supporting the <![CDATA[<color=orange>Sun Station</color>]]>’s construction, but here we are.</Text>
	</TextBlock>
	<TextBlock>
		<ID>6</ID>
		<ParentID>3</ParentID>
